      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "If no one has any better ideas (this is a shot in the dark) maybe it would be helpful to know what happens if you bring down this node's network connection to force disconnection from all your peers, and then bring your network connection back up.  Perhaps that would give us a clue as to whether it could be an inconsistency with mapBlocksInFlight (ie if it is unable to sync even after disconnecting from all peers), or if it does sync, maybe that would be a hint that one of your peers is triggering an issue that disconnecting from them resolves?\n",
